qualities.name: Friendliness Level
qualities.description: The degree to which the interviewer's tone and demeanor are friendly and welcoming. Options may include: High, Medium, Low.

qualities.name: Technical Proficiency
qualities.description: The level of technical knowledge and expertise possessed by the interviewer. Options may include: High, Medium, Low.

qualities.name: Professionalism Rating
qualities.description: The extent to which the interviewer adheres to professional standards and conducts the interview in a formal manner. Options may include: High, Medium, Low.

qualities.name: Empathy Level
qualities.description: The degree to which the interviewer demonstrates understanding and compassion towards the interviewee's experiences and challenges. Options may include: High, Medium, Low.

qualities.name: Feedback Provision Skill
qualities.description: The proficiency of the interviewer in providing constructive feedback to the interviewee, helping them understand areas for improvement. Options may include: High, Medium, Low.
